      </introduction>
      <task>
        <statement><p><m>\frac{\sin{x} + \tan{x}}{1 + \cos{x}} = \frac{\sin{(2x)}}{2 \cos^2{x}}</m></p></statement>
        <hint><p>start with both sides, double-angle identity, clear denominators, cancel</p></hint>
      </task>
