    <exercise>
      <title>Tangent Expression</title>
      <statement><p>Given that <m>\csc\theta=\frac{b}{x}</m> and <m>\theta</m> is in quadrant <m>2</m>, find an expression for <m>\tan 2\theta</m> in terms of <m>x</m>.</p></statement>
      <hint><p><m>\tan 2\theta=\frac{2\tan\theta}{1-\tan^2\theta}</m>, and simplify the complex fraction</p></hint>
      <answer><p><m>\tan 2\theta=-\frac{2x\sqrt{b^2-x^2}}{b^2-2x^2}</m></p></answer>
